覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3778a7d6327d725ab194c51601b70c2d88588a30","tid":1746050,"uid":322230,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAK1bvJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwAK1bvJ.jpg&h=fce4d266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條友係咩人自己睇"},{"pid":"2a114e380919ea2d155ab3224d1229c7308e2c38","tid":1746050,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51f89a35401549318c11ce8c28e251576cef6339","tid":1746050,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"945a18cdd8eb1b072b267a8d712af09c393e3f95","tid":1746050,"uid":281754,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"絕對正確,咩叫做血債票還on撚9"},{"pid":"fc15635d42c39ba00b0de28e4868f010a7a80724","tid":1746050,"uid":281754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"義士的血不是這樣用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a232722943af6eac89b850e7187d2c07d3b18030","tid":1746050,"uid":123933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"利申：我係教徒。<br />\n我會投票，亦會含淚投民主派。<br />\n<br />\n但希望大家明白，香港選舉制度，只係為資源。<br />\n贏輸與否，其實並無大分別。<br />\n香港個問題係個制度到，現行嘅選舉只係一個俾中共用嚟掩飾出面一切正常嘅工具。<br />\n<br />\n況且，血債只能血償，絕不能票償。<br />\n監就手足坐，錢就泛民議員代，哈哈。<br />\n<br />\n除非泛民肯應承贏咗後將資源繼續支持抗爭運動，否則我都會繼續屌泛民。"},{"pid":"f69855e6c302207ece7ff82a6712d3f46932129f","tid":1746050,"uid":6334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"我本土撚<br />\n區選會比面投飯民<br />\n但血債票償真係好撚on9<br />\n人命一定要用人命還<br />\n三萬曱甴，政府高官，共產黨<br />\n你地滿手鮮血，終有一日會自食其果"},{"pid":"e74e05d10c0a2963d09691bfdbf401201b9112e2","tid":1746050,"uid":1